n</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-M%E1%BA%ABn-T%C3%BAc/poem-vd4FPoMpc9d9HsKcrFQ15w">Tặng Mẫn Túc - 贈敏肅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem--LsKiQ1eOygSMk7fNhUr8w">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhị đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第二段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A0n/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-sy-sKX-ta9pLXlJ63LXSbg">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A0n/author-eiEvt-dUxPC4DoEX4jKnEg">Vương Bàn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C5%A9-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mhqMJz3rm6EkpRr3HxYIjw">Vũ hành - 雨行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
